et/sigpics/ribbon_small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Questions about Armor Crafting *midgard*</span><hr size=1> Ok, got a RL friend (read: room mate) working on Armor smithing, trying to task his way.<br>
